WEBVTT

00:00:14.517 --> 00:00:17.089
Wouldn't it be great if we could be

00:00:17.113 --> 00:00:18.270
invisible?

00:00:18.294 --> 00:00:19.049
Ha, right?

00:00:19.073 --> 00:00:21.550
I mean, we could spy on people
without being noticed

00:00:21.574 --> 00:00:22.885
and do whatever we want

00:00:22.909 --> 00:00:25.505
without being held responsible.

00:00:25.529 --> 00:00:27.195
Now, magicians have figured out

00:00:27.219 --> 00:00:29.868
how to utilize full-sized
mirrors to bend light

00:00:29.892 --> 00:00:34.534
in order to create disappearing illusions.